		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top">
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Wed, Feb 21st 9:01 AM2001 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class=sm>IP: Logged</span> | <a class=sm href="/db/classes.html?class=10&mid=9827100694532&num=4&page=&post=1&replyto=9827640885474"><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=11 width=17> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=9827640885474></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.66]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Anonymous&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I use my bow allot however I do not depend on it for one main reason.&nbsp;&nbsp;Verant has not fixed the LOS problems.  I have been on the slightest of inclines and declines only to have my arrow fire into nothingness.  No hit, no miss, no nothing.  They just vanish!!  As for silvertip arrows, I never make or use them.  It's just too expensive and you can't recover the arrows.  Add that LOS problem and it's a huge waste of plats.  I strictly use the cheapest possible arrows and make lots of them.  With my trusty raincaller *GRIN* I hit for 21 normally and 44 critical if I actually hit.  I have not had much success on yellow or red con due to mega resistance to my roots and/or snares but I do take down blue and even cons with little or no hp loss.  I love my bow and do hope verant will fix and maybe even improve the bow for us.  I do say max your fletching and archery if you are a ranger.  Good hunting all!!</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
